{"tid":1534140,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[雲加會戰勝歸來]雲爺爺：我會復出再做教練","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:01:07.000Z","uid":103207,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"345d0f832e38c512d3a03cc0dc0faf712f8b50df","tid":1534140,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"雲格：執教時我隔絕了全世界 我會復出再做教練<br />\n雲格稱自己還會出山執教<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  球壇出名教頭雲格在離開阿仙奴後，一直賦閒在家。如今雲格公開透露，自己會復出執教。<br />\n<br />\n  雲格稱：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我拒絕了很多不錯的執教機會，因為我還沒覺得我已經準備好了。或許我已經意識到了，當我執教的時候，我一直倒在我自己的泡沫裡，一直遠離著整個世界。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n  「這讓我同整個世界都有了距離，<span style=\"color: red;\">也讓我有些猶豫，猶豫是否要這麼快跳回執教的火坑。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n  「<span style=\"color: red;\">我在沒有打擾的情況下執教了35年。現在我有機會離開了那個泡沫，睜開我的雙眼去看世界，慢慢享受這一切。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n  「<span style=\"color: red;\">你們還會在教練席上看到我的，就是不知道會是什麼時候。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n早過daddy返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51adf65258699de6829f28d64b01c0533c3f7630","tid":1534140,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c065917cd26a23db195fcf98c67c5389ea8239c","tid":1534140,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:18:10.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2a1dfc1fbed58e4201b2059c3a7701a0824fc8","tid":1534140,"uid":27438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:33:52.000Z","msg":"巴塞？"},{"pid":"01b914418972e81b539025e2985f9fa953b66d84","tid":1534140,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"愛狗差唔多收皮.<br />\n爺爺等機會皇者回歸"},{"pid":"45de2246abc099c7882b0ac05bba08bfdd7b51eb","tid":1534140,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score"